members.member:
Parser implements a recursive-descent parser for the following grammar:
E -> T OR E | T T -> F AND T | F F -> ID EQ VALUE | ( E )
E = Expression (ANDs and ORs) T = Term (ANDs only) F = Clause ID = Identifier (token) EQ = EQ operator (token) VALUE = value (token) OR = OR operator (token) AND = AND operator (token) ( and ) are also terminals (tokens)
